1933;;By Candlelight;;American;;James Whale;;Elissa Landi, Paul Lukas;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/By_Candlelight;;During a European train journey, a nobleman's butler Josef (Paul Lukas) is mistaken for his employer Prince Alfred von Rommer (Nils Asther) by a beautiful woman, Marie (Elissa Landi), and he does nothing to disillusion her. In due course, the Prince himself arrives and is mistaken for his servant.